{120}
                          The Alchemist's Workshop
{300}
The Alchemist's Workshop can be found by going east on the stream south of the
gnome village.  Be prepared to talk to the mobs and write down the clues that
they give you (there are too many to remember).  Words in all caps are likely
to be good conversation starters.

Do not trust the hints given to you by other PCs because the clues and the
solutions to quests will vary from person to person.  Be prepared to use your
brain a little bit if you want to learn how to make gold and enter the guild
of Alchemists.
~

