~
>speech_prog troubles~
if quest (10,3,$n) == 0
  say Troubles?!  Just look around.
  say It was Politics that took all I have.
  say Now I have to eke out a living trying to
  say practice my art with sub-standard materials
  say and worthless apprentices.
  say Somehow an experiment got out of control and
  say those creatures took over my house.
  say I haven't been in it for years.
  sigh 
endif
~
>speech_prog transmutation~
